  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Driving in the EU from 1 January 2021: UK licence holders living in the EU
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">You must exchange your UK driving licence before 31 December 2020.</p>

  </div>
</div>

